<i>noun</i>: 상고머리 [상고머리] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>상고머리 [상고머리]</dt><br>
<dd>crew cut; flattop</dd><br>
<dd>앞머리와 정수리 부분을 남기고 옆머리와 뒷머리를 짧게 깎은 머리 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A hair style of which the bangs and top of the head are left as they are and the sides and back are shaved short.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>